'''hindu dhorm'''' ([[somskrit bhas|somskrit]]: sonaton dhorm')zogalem sokodd dhormampoxinem pornem dhorm' ass। hem dkxinn axialem niz dhorm' ani bohusonkhyelem dhorm'। hem ved adharit dhorm', vingodd-vingodd onuxtthan, mot, pod'dhotio, somprodai ani dorxon ott'ttu korunu ass। vixvasokangelem sonkhyeri hem zogantulem tisrem vhodd dhorm' ass। yodyopi hantum most devi-deutangeli puza zat'ta, bod'd mhonnleri hem ekixvorovadi dhorm' ass। onuyayi onusar hem zogantulem tisrem vhodd dhorm' ass। hajjim 828 orob onuyayi [[bharot]]antum, 23 orob [[nepall]]antum, 14 orob [[bangladex]]antum ani 3.3 orob [[bali]], [[inddonexia]]ntum assoti। 

[[hindu xastr]]alem most vafmoi [[xruti]] othva [[smriti]]ntum vingodd kel'lolem ass। him vafmoi [[onuxtthan]], [[tot'tvovad]] ani [[purann]]avixoyari assoti ani dhorm' onusar koxxi jiychem hem sangtati। hantum prai, moht'tv ani odhikaravixoyari [[ved]] sokdantum vhodd assoti। [[upnixod]], mohakauy [[ramainn]] ani [[mohabharot]] ony vhodd vafmoi। mohabharotari adharit xastr [[bhagoud gita]] haka chodd moht'tv asta।

