==ugom'==

hindu hem utr,[[bharti-i upmohadvip]]alem vaivy bodik vhamvtolem [[sindhu nhoyim]]thamvunu ailam। hindu hem namv, mukhari, orbi utr '''ol-hind''', orthat sindhu nhoyilem peltoddieri rabtolim zon, mhunnu prosid'dh zal'lem। 13xotok i. Thamyi '''hindustan''' (hinduvangeli bhumi) hem bhartak poreayi namvadhik namv mell'lem। 

adlem kalantum '''hindu''' bharti-i upmohadvipari rabtole, dhorm' khonchem-i asso, sokodd zonank appoitolinti। 18 xotok i.Lem koddekalantum yuropi-i zonamni bharti-i dhormangelem onusoronn kortolenk hindu mhunnu appomvochek suru kel'lem। maggiri hindu dhormalem veakhea '''udeyontilem dhorm' (kristamv,yohudi, islam') nat'tilem ani vedanthamvunu yenit'tilem dhorm' (boud'dh, zoin, sikh)hanka soddunu bharti-i pallale zonangele dhorm'''' oxxi zal'lem।

==itihasu==

adlem bharti-i dhormalem promann [[horppa kal]]antum (5500-2600 i.Pu) mellta। adihindu dhorm' 1500-500 i.Pu.Lem onuxtthanank appoitati। aizochem hindu dhorm' vedanthamvunu ailem (1700-1100)। voidik onuxtthanantum [[indr]], [[vorunn]], [[ogni]] oxxi prakritik xoktiangelem puzu ani [[som']] vidhi zat'tolem। yogone ani voidik montrochcharoi zat'tolem। tauvolli deusthan ani vigroh naऽxilinti। voidik dhorm' ani [[majdayasna/zortoxtti dhorm']]antum ani kelvu [[bharti-i-yuropi-i dhorm']]antum most somanote ass।

isvi purvalem koddekalantum ani isvilem adle kalantum [[ramainn]] ani [[mohabharot]] him vhodd somskrit upneas boromvunu ailim। kodderi devi-deutangelim, monuxamott'ttu mellap ani doiteamott'ttu zuzhavixoyari sangtolim, [[purann]] ailim।

tin vhodd prourtonamni hindu vicharak novem dik dakkomyolem- upnixodik, zoin ani boud'dh manyotangelem sokodd bhartantum prosar। [[mohavir]] (zoinangelim 24. [[tirthonkor]]) ani [[bud'dh]] ([[boud'dh dhorm']]alim somsthapok) hamni xikkomyolem ki mokx melluk vedank ani zati pod'dhotik svikarochem ogty na। bud'dhalem mukhari vochchuku hemvy sanglem ki atma ani devalem aschem onauxyok। 200 i.Ntum [[hindu sid'dhant]]alem (Hindu Philosophy) most dorxonantum (Hindu Schools of Thought) vorgikoronn zal'lem।

