===gupt kall===

gupt kalla uprant somskritalem sthan unnem zamvunu prokrit mukhari ailem। vedangelem sthan gounn zamvunu purann-adharit, yeklle promann mhunnu dhoried oxxi, dhormalem zolm' zal'lem। brahmonn ani dhormoxastr kendrit hindu dhormantum porivrton suru zal'lem।

===islamalem kall===

7. Xotok i.Ntum orob poinnariamni sindh jikunu islam' bharti-i upmohadvipari haddlem। hem kalantum boud'dh dhormalem odhogoti suru zal'lem ani most hindu zonamni islam' svikarolem। ourongojeb mhonnke most muslim' razamni deusthanam bhet'tunu muslman nat'tilancheri onyai kel'lem। yodyopi [[raza okbor]] mhonnke kelvu raza sohixnnu axxilim। [[ramanuzachary]], [[madhvachary]], [[choitny mohaprobhu]] hangelem probhavanimit'ti hindu dhormantum vhodd porivrton ailem। [[adi xonkrachary]]anem kelvu xotkamfudde [[nirgunn brohmonn]]alem suru kel'lelem onuxtthanank soddunu sulobh poddtolem [[vixnnu ovtar]]angele hamni [[bhokti somprodai]]ale marganem onuxtthan suru kel'lem। 


==ixvor==

hindu dhormantum ixvoralim vingddovingodd sid'dhant assoti; [[ekixvorovad]] (monotheism), [[bohuixvorovad]] (polytheism), [[sankhy]] (panentheism),[[odvoit]] (pantheism), [[yog]] (monism) ani [[nirixvorovad]] (atheism)। zon tat'tangele dorxona onusar onuxtthan kortati। 

most hindu zon atma, apnnamlem bod'd svorup, haka xaxvot lektati। [[odvoit vedant]] dorxona onusar ho atma ixvora thamvunu vingodd na। odvoit mhonnta ki monuxojlmalem dhyey, apnnamlo atma ixvor zomv ass, hem kollchem ass। yodyopi, upnixod mhonntati ki apnnank atmalem zannvai zal'lem, ani brohma ott'ttu sombondh koll'leri aponn mokx pamvta।

dvoit dorxon anisar brohm' vingodd vyoktimt'tv ass ani dvoit onuyayi taka somprodaya onusar [[brohm']], [[vixnnu]], [[xiv]] othva [[xokti]] mhunnu pujtati। 

==axromodhrm'==

protiekollalem jivitalim char bindu assoti। 
* [[brohmochreaxrom']]- hem char voros dhokkunu ottra vorsantham-i asta। hantum monuxanem matr xikka ani tajjenkhat'tiri brohmochry pallka। hem cherudduponna dhokkunu tornnayalem suruve tham-i asta।
* [[grihostaxrom']]- hem tornnayalem modhyokallantum, bohux: prai 25-30tham-i, yet'ta। hantum ekllanem vorddik koried ani cherudduvank zolm' dimvyed।
* [[vonprosthaxrom']]- hem kall 65-70 uprant suru zat'ta। hantum ekllanem sontuxtt zamvka ani teag koruk xikka। 
* [[somneasaxrom']] - hantum monuxanem sompurnn teag korunu deukareantum lagka।

==choturvornnaxrom'==

haka aizochem poreayi utr '''zati''' ass। bod'd mhonnleri choturvornnaxrom' hem '''chotur''' orthat '''char''' ani '''vornn''' orthant '''bonn'nn''' he utranthamvunu yet'ta।

* [[brahmonn]]
* [[kxotriy]]
* [[voixy]]
* [[kxudr]]
him char vornn assoti।

vedkalantum him vornn protiekolle monuxalim char gunnodhrm' oxxi lektolinti। rigvedantum boromylam-
<big>''zonmona zaite kxudr: somskarat dviz uchyote। vidyoya yati viprotvam' brohm' zanati iti brahmonn:।। ''</big> 

zolma vellari protielo kxudr (xuny) asta। somskaramnimit'ti taka dusrem zolm' mellta (dviz)। vidyenem to budhvont zat'ta। hamnem taka brohm' kollta ani to brahmonn (brohm' konnank kollta) zat'ta। aiji him utr zativachok zal'lanti।

==solla somskar==

somskar jiunantule moht'tvalem binduvangelim protik assoti ani mhunnu tangelem achronn korka। protyokx-oprotyokx hantum pitrangelem, mhalgoddangelem ani mogachangelem ul'lekh othva sohbhag zat'ta। him assoti-

* <big>prosou somskar</big>

** [[gorbhodan]] - darlanem ani bailenem cherudduva khat'tiri ott'ttu yemvchem।

** [[ful'la mollop]] - gorbhalim lokxonn disleri '''pumsoun''' ani '''simantonoin''' zat'ta। hem prosvalem panchvem, satvem, nouvem masantum kortati।

* <big>cherudduponn somskar</big> 

** [[barso]] zolma uprantolem kallak '''soir''' (zonon oxouch) mhonntati ani hem ikra dis asta। ikrovem disari avusu, cheruddu ani kuttmalem xud'dhi khat'tiri '''grih xanti''' kortati। '''ponchgauy praxon'''a upranti '''soir''' mugdoxita। cherudduvalo barso zat'ta। fudde zolma uprant sohvem disari '''sot'ti (xoxtthi) puzu kortolinti। aizochem kallari hem most unnem zal'lam।

** [[dantollio]] haka somskritantum on'nopraxon mhonntati। chol'liankhat'tiri hem attvem, dhavem, baravem (oz) masantum ani chol'lienkhat'tiri panchvem, satvem, nouvem (som') masantum zat'ta। 

** [[zaull kaddchem]] chol'liangelem poilem ailelem kems poilem, dusrem vorsantum kaddtati।

** [[kan topchem]] cherudduvalem kan 12vem othva 16vem disari, 6vem, 7vem othva 8vem masari na zol'leri 1lem,3rem,5vem,7vem,9vem vorsari toptati। chol'liangelem ujje kan ani chol'liengelem davem kan toptati।










